replies.content:
Thank you all for the valuable insights! @Dr. Chen, your compliance approach is exactly what we need. We'll definitely consider blockchain for audit trails.

@Mark, LoRaWAN sounds promising - would love to learn more about your middleware solution.

@Sarah, our current alert system is basic email/SMS. Planning to implement:
1. Tiered alert levels
2. Mobile app notifications
3. Automated escalation after 15 minutes

@James, great point about SPC. We're currently evaluating analytics platforms that support these capabilities.

Additional question: How do you handle sensor calibration and verification?
